<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Software development freelancing activities</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"constrained"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>According to <a href="https://www.dictionary.com/browse/activity\">Dictionary.com an activity</a> is </p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true} -->
<ol><!-- wp:list-item {"fontSize":"small"} -->
<li class="has-small-font-size">the <strong>state</strong> or quality of <strong>being active</strong>:</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item {"fontSize":"small"} -->
<li class="has-small-font-size"><em>There was not much activity in the stock market today. He doesn't have enough physical activity in his life.</em></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item {"fontSize":"small"} -->
<li class="has-small-font-size"><strong>a specific deed, action, function, or sphere of action</strong>:<em>social activities.</em></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>
<!-- /wp:list --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>So, if you want to be a "<strong>software"</strong> "<strong>development"</strong> "<strong>freelancer"</strong> you need these kinds of activities:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Learning</strong>: gaining the knowledge to understand software.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Training</strong>: practicing, getting evaluated and coached.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Hiring</strong>: finding a job and establishing a contract.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Planning your work:</strong> figuring out how you are going to do the work, when, and reporting your plan.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Equiping</strong>: getting the tools and platforms needed.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Developing</strong>: building, completing, testing and documenting.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Delivering</strong>: handing it over to your client.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Getting paid</strong>: completing the contract, satisfying the client, and getting the pay you have earned.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Rinse and repeat.</strong></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>You <strong>can't</strong> do these things by yourself!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>A <strong>learner</strong> needs a <strong>teacher</strong>.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>A <strong>trainee</strong> needs a trainer or <strong>mentor</strong>.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>A <strong>freelancer</strong> needs a <strong>client</strong> with a <strong>job</strong>.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>A <strong>planner</strong> needs many things:  decomposition, stages of work, planning, documenting, reviewing, coordinating...</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Equipping</strong> requires a <strong>source</strong> of tools, platforms, and process knowledge to be ready to do the job.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Developing</strong> is a whole process in itself, covered elsewhere on this site.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Delivery</strong> requires a <strong>repository</strong> to document your process and contain your deliverables so they can be used by the client or others.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Getting paid</strong> requires coordination with the client, an escrow agent, a funds transfer agent, and your bank.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Rinse and repeat</strong> requires <strong>learning</strong> from one job and the <strong>courage</strong> and <strong>determination</strong> to start all over again. </li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>You can do this!</strong>  This site will lead you to all of these things and you can be a success. </p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

